properties.areaDesc: Taiya Inlet and Klondike Highway; Haines Borough and Lynn Canal
properties.headline: Winter Storm Warning issued January 25 at 5:11AM AKST until January 26 at 9:00PM AKST by NWS Juneau AK
properties.description:
* WHAT...Heavy snow expected. Total snow accumulations of 10 to
22 inches.

* WHERE...Taiya Inlet and Klondike Highway and Haines Borough
and Lynn Canal.

* WHEN...From 6 PM this evening to 9 PM AKST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Travel could be very difficult to impossible. Heavy
wet snow will be difficult to manage.
properties.instruction:
If you must travel, keep an extra flashlight, food, and water in
your vehicle in case of an emergency.

For the latest road conditions call 5 1 1 or visit
511.alaska.gov.

NWSheadline: WINTER STORM WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 6 PM THIS EVENING TO 9 PM AKST SUNDAY FOR NORTHERN INNER CHANNELS
